cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and the modeling of social biases and stereotypes in language. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning and inference, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with social implications and power differentials, which could fall under categories such as cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
